snippet.title: MotoGP™21 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The most authentic and realistic MotoGP™ experience is coming.
Be ready to live the emotions of the official 2021 season, managing all the aspects of your race, like a real champion. MotoGP™21 will be out on April 22.
